726734f-a.title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - 60th Drive
726734f-a.text:
Fresh Pond Rd. (center of view), north from about 60th Drive, showing
in the center of view the Richard Way house located at the S.W. corner
of 59th Drive and Fresh Pond Road. This low peaked roof structure was
not in existence in 1929.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726733f-a.title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - 60th Drive
726733f-a.text:
Fresh Pond Road, at 60th Drive, showing the surrounding
area before it was developed. Note the old frame dwellings
on the left and rows of new brick houses in the right back-
ground.
M.4 -22-~NS
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  About 1922
